      "content": "that's a good start. i want to make sure the essay doesn't just sound like a list of points but really exposes why the other side's views are problematic. specifically, can you add a section that critiques the idea of meritocracy? i want to show how meritocracy is actually just a way to justify existing racial hierarchies and keep the status quo going. how should i frame that to make it sound most convincing?",
